{"tid":792644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我應唔應該裸辭好","createTime":"2018-08-24T16:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T10:10:49.000Z","uid":67208,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6580745cb8c5695dd34f366b965156bfa91828d2","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:47:18.000Z","msg":"小弟今年32 做緊份文職3年幾<br />\n一直都想轉工 但奈何又轉唔成<br />\n覺得份工返到好悶 令到個人好冇衝勁<br />\n返到公司 有時唉聲嘆氣<br />\n&ldquo;唉 點解我仲做緊呢到&rdquo;<br />\n份工人工比上不足 3皮幾4皮<br />\n要加人工多就要轉工 但又轉唔到<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下 原來就黎2018年9月<br />\n呢9個月 我做過啲咩呢 <br />\n好似好白過 <br />\n<br />\n又未有老婆仔女要養 女友又溝唔到<br />\n<br />\n好似一日復一日 人生呢幾年好似過得好快<br />\n<br />\n亦好似白白流逝<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻有少少想辭職去旅行<br />\n但又好似好唔腳踏實地<br />\n都三十幾歲人仲搞呢啲野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實心入面好迷惘 好多問號"},{"pid":"551b01139ed942ab1b92205b3367bfe23e749901","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T16:52:40.000Z","msg":"眼見身邊啲人生活充實 又多活動玩<br />\n自己就生活暗淡無光 日日返屋企<br />\n朋友又唔多個<br />\n唉<br />\n<br />\n又見有啲中有家庭有兒女<br />\n起碼每日都有意義啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bcd0cc69da97f236a37f69334066852578be4b","tid":792644,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:08:19.000Z","msg":"part time degree &gt; 考aco"},{"pid":"b9371eeba074793372b977e106a755f81e5f854b","tid":792644,"uid":208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔係你份工問題 係你識唔到人既問題 轉工未必解決到你面對既問題"},{"pid":"8c252efc3c918993f11f524204406cacb236a7d3","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9371eeba074793372b977e106a755f81e5f854b","tid":792644,"uid":208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"唔係你份工問題 係你識唔到人既問題 轉工未必解決到你面對既問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"其實都係 <br />\n好似唔會同人熟絡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c436ee32dd9b47b612dd63ca17cf7733be9938fb","tid":792644,"uid":69189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"我又係32歲，做到好頹，有無tg傾？"},{"pid":"ca7b198bbd708c22fda9f4a32a7f79477f13aa3e","tid":792644,"uid":82714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"既然都冇咩大顧慮 點解唔行出自己個comfort zone?"},{"pid":"5ea440832938c087af23b382d3e4df2221d5b1a5","tid":792644,"uid":82714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"多口問句 點解轉唔到工？"},{"pid":"3ac5b6aa3e4d357fb3fcadb247e353db5d2a340c","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c436ee32dd9b47b612dd63ca17cf7733be9938fb","tid":792644,"uid":69189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"我又係32歲，做到好頹，有無tg傾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:07:51.000Z","msg":"你留啦"},{"pid":"c89eceeca022c25a6e1f156f863b61c6c0c3935d","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca7b198bbd708c22fda9f4a32a7f79477f13aa3e","tid":792644,"uid":82714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:00:53.000Z","msg":"既然都冇咩大顧慮 點解唔行出自己個comfort zone?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"好似做緊一啲&ldquo;浪費&rdquo;時間嘅野<br />\n當然如果我唔裸辭 都唔代表我會開心啲 會識到囡 <br />\n都係營營役役 儲到多啲錢咁<br />\n<br />\n其實我幾年前都試過裸辭去旅行<br />\n但嗰陣好似仲後生 好多理由說服自己<br />\n什麼夢想 什麼一生人一次"},{"pid":"e325feae47f5ebcdb2c69c3f9f0ecb21b07b87e1","tid":792644,"uid":67208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea440832938c087af23b382d3e4df2221d5b1a5","tid":792644,"uid":82714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"多口問句 點解轉唔到工？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T01:14:08.000Z","msg":"一來啲工好似唔多啱心水<br />\n恃住自己有份工就會揀擇啲<br />\n<br />\n到我apply完有得見嗰